  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\n\r\nCurrently OpenZeppelin Contracts only builds with Node.js version 12, and that version is [not under active development by vendor](https://nodejs.org/en/about/releases/).\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\n\r\n- [ ] Set a policy that OpenZeppelin Contracts is supported on Node.js 12 and that support for \"ACTIVE\" and \"CURRENT\" versions of Node.js is desired (i.e. pull requests welcome)\r\n   - [ ] Announce this policy on main README, DOCUMENTATION or other authoritative place\r\n- [ ] Update GitHub Actions build script to implement a matrix build strategy\r\n- [ ] Mark versions other than version 12 as `continue-on-error`\r\n\r\nAn example of this matrix strategy and `continue-on-error` is implemented at https://github.com/bovigo/vfsStream/blob/d66bb85a6738288a833955c36586f2eb4a176cf5/.github/workflows/runTests.yml\r\n",
